<view class="screen">
  <view class="section model-head">
    <view class="title-lg">七指标 Kcact 模型</view>
    <view class="body muted">以 PML-V2.2a ETa / ERA5 ET0 构造 Kcact 标签，七指标与标签在同一 8 日窗口内对齐。</view>
    <view class="model-card-grid">
      <view wx:for="{{modelCards}}" wx:key="label" class="model-card">
        <view class="caption muted">{{item.label}}</view>
        <view class="model-card-value">{{item.value}}</view>
        <view class="caption muted">{{item.unit}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="title-md">选用指标</view>
    <view class="chip-grid">
      <view wx:for="{{chips}}" wx:key="*this" class="model-chip">{{item}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="row between">
      <view class="title-md">特征贡献排序</view>
      <view class="caption muted">相对贡献示意</view>
    </view>

    <view class="feature-list">
      <view wx:for="{{features}}" wx:key="name" class="feature-row">
        <view class="feature-name">{{item.name}}</view>
        <view class="feature-track">
          <view class="feature-fill {{item.tone}}" style="width: {{item.score}}%;"></view>
        </view>
        <view class="feature-score">{{item.score}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="title-md">逐年留一年验证</view>
    <view class="year-list">
      <view wx:for="{{yearly}}" wx:key="year" class="year-row">
        <view class="year-name">{{item.year}}</view>
        <view class="year-track"><view class="year-fill" style="width: {{item.score}}%;"></view></view>
        <view class="year-r2">R² {{item.r2}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="title-md">建模说明</view>
    <view class="body muted note">模型训练样本为 2019–2024 年华北平原夏玉米，PML 与 ERA5、S2、SM 均按稳定经纬度键和同一 8 日窗口对齐，再统一到 0.1° 格网训练；不使用未来窗口或全年统计特征。</view>
  </view>
</view>
